{"tid":2029642,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港=街亭、馬謖=寶寶龍+腳震寧","createTime":"2020-05-22T10:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T02:19:06.000Z","uid":21678,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8214d9a91852bb49e501b2ce3f06637bdebc039e","tid":2029642,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:32:08.000Z","msg":"對號入座<br />\n如果香港就係街亭、馬謖就係寶寶龍+駱腳震寧<br />\n<br />\n講返少少典故<br />\n馬謖係蜀國參軍<br />\n學業彪炳而且才華洋溢，深受諸葛亮賞識<br />\n諸葛絕地反擊，揮軍北伐打曹營<br />\n將守響祁山嘅魏軍打得節節敗退<br />\n連祁山北邊嘅天水、南岸、安定三個邵紛紛向曹魏叛變<br />\n一手好牌，可謂大勢在握<br />\n<br />\n當諸葛大軍進駐祁山，諗住派一支精兵去守住街亭<br />\n其他將領都提議由魏延同吳懿擔任主將<br />\n點知係諸葛亮硬係安插一個諸葛派嘅人落去做呢個位<br />\n只將魏延王平高翔列為助手<br />\n<br />\n結果大家都清楚<br />\n馬謖呢條冇乜經驗嘅人，畀人困咗響山上便，畀人斷水＋燒山<br />\n最後馬謖棄兵而逃<br />\n街亭失守，北伐大軍兵敗如山倒<br />\n馬謖正宗一個累全家<br />\n<br />\n反觀今日<br />\n駱夏呢兩條冇打過國際線嘅柒頭<br />\n紙上談兵，suggest 習敗敗呢條變奏廿三條嘅橋<br />\n香港會唔會好似街亭咁畀美帝打到片甲不留<br />\n<br />\n大家就睇吓車公今劑又有幾準"},{"pid":"c841d5e09ba23212c2c8e40050a21c964caa10e0","tid":2029642,"uid":269515,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:33:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MiJO5UK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMiJO5UK.jpg&h=7797c282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【如果你覺得好無力，不妨諗下...難道習近平又過得好好？】<br />\n<br />\n「黎明前嘅黑暗係最黑暗」係句好詩意嘅說話。如果通俗少少講，就係：有打開機都知，隻boss開始暴走放大招嘅時候，其實就係佢殘血就死之時。<br />\n中共之所以呢個時候推國安法，唔係因為佢管治能力有幾高明或者幾有作為，而係相反，正正顯示到佢地已經冇招。一個喺管治上已經無招可用嘅政權，敗亡亦不過係時候問題。"},{"pid":"5952018189595043df6408cac947f8df721c7f6f","tid":2029642,"uid":166405,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:34:03.000Z","msg":"郭嘉巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf899c78ccb595fcbdcc767868fbad85903f28d","tid":2029642,"uid":21678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:34:04.000Z","msg":"車公加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030633557276cefec4e0379154ff92d52536ead6","tid":2029642,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:34:27.000Z","msg":"馬謖=泛民"},{"pid":"2e1fd7080f99ebba6f0eaa659c0d7f3399100745","tid":2029642,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:34:43.000Z","msg":"奉孝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc3a92e25cabb4d33311421b5f5a5675e71e347","tid":2029642,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:35:00.000Z","msg":"期待sanctions <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daad0ebcfdfe6c2a165d76bd66c70f31c1ef20d3","tid":2029642,"uid":39277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:36:26.000Z","msg":"寶寶龍=趙括<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870288651836f182bc6874cbe44d7187d2006f1c","tid":2029642,"uid":307398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff063eb4af233f740066bc1ea7d7c86132e6d0fc","tid":2029642,"uid":42982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:40:10.000Z","msg":"泛民=李嚴"},{"pid":"a15a7773cc1ee4f9d2c144e2e0647c7f814ff6bc","tid":2029642,"uid":21678,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"030633557276cefec4e0379154ff92d52536ead6","tid":2029642,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:34:27.000Z","msg":"馬謖=泛民"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:42:31.000Z","msg":"請問泛民幾時「才華洋溢」過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"dd8c53c826955e595889ac496740baa450167cfa","tid":2029642,"uid":293242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:44:59.000Z","msg":"郭嘉巴<