,"tid":2029642,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:16:28.000Z","msg":"因為馬謖王平未轉正，只係轉正左個蘿莉夏侯姬"},{"pid":"c6142c98a499420f441c77b58630bc55d7fb6aff","tid":2029642,"uid":270872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69bbb5042922b1d6fa249773bc1dba8bd1941ddd","tid":2029642,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c89f2e009a09bd0aa10ae5741ef77ea6fc83a085","tid":2029642,"uid":270872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:53:28.000Z","msg":"車公好準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:04:05.000Z","msg":"仲要好黃<br />\n車公巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:28:23.000Z","msg":"黃色神仙圈"},{"pid":"126296e4d682d2f7591c913cc09fd1b76eff5ec4","tid":2029642,"uid":23574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:29:50.000Z","msg":"奉孝巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa76703894ec70843971d244b21649d7609fda8","tid":2029642,"uid":23574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:34:04.000Z","msg":"習種往往有能力將一手好牌玩爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果佢繼續胡溫嗰期滔光養晦溫水煮蛙<br />\n今日唔止香港<br />\n全世界好多地方應該都會係比中共控制"},{"pid":"df46c7ee0e11072c15ba0aee8f4a30cba23e90ce","tid":2029642,"uid":33473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得馬謖係777<br />\n一個自傲唔聽人講的人<br />\n可能曾經係唔同位置做得ok<br />\n例如777做公務員同政務司不過不失<br />\n年年考第一<br />\n馬謖都係曾經獻計得諸葛亮稱讚<br />\n但衰乜？衰一朝得志恃才傲物<br />\n唔聽人講又死牛一面頸<br />\n王平叫佢唔好上山<br />\n佢覺得全世界唔岩係佢岩<br />\n咁岩諸葛亮比左佢領軍<br />\n就好似777係做凸手咁<br />\n咁衰左一獲大囉<br />\n千年道行一朝喪<br />\n<br />\n而且斷送的係蜀國諸葛亮第一次北伐<br />\n形勢最好的一次<br />\n正如777斷送左香港呢個一國兩制的首例<br />\n520蔡英文直接了當收左和平統一皮"},{"pid":"b8701cf9cbffa85353be6682fe174e852e5aae9a","tid":2029642,"uid":10176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:35:05.000Z","msg":"刁大大=劉禪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f6043e99aa910a4f55dd7ce49cfa2b6187da4d","tid":2029642,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:04:52.000Z","msg":"車公"},{"pid":"aca2ecae59bd3d4133a02ab9b62447f5bf50e4af","tid":2029642,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:08:30.000Z","msg":"奉孝巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}